{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"659","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"企業出版永續報告 EPS高於台股平均值","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>2020-03-25 05:30</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E6%B0%B8%E7%BA%8CCSR.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 455px;' />&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>（取自<span lang='EN-US'>CSRone</span>永續觀點臉書）</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<hr />\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>去年<span lang='EN-US'>556</span>家公司出版<span lang='EN-US'>CSR </span>上市櫃占<span lang='EN-US'>92.3%</span></span></strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>〔記者陳永吉／台北報導〕根據<span lang='EN-US'>CSRone</span>永續智庫出版的《<span lang='EN-US'>2020</span>台灣暨亞太永續報告現況與趨勢》專書統計，台灣去年共有<span lang='EN-US'>556</span>家公司出版<span lang='EN-US'>CSR</span>（企業永續報告書），其中上市櫃公司占了<span lang='EN-US'>92.3%</span>。值得注意的是，有出版<span lang='EN-US'>CSR</span>的公司，不只<span lang='EN-US'>EPS</span>（每股稅後盈餘）高於台股平均值，<span lang='EN-US'>ROE</span>（股東權益報酬率）連<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>年也高於台股平均表現。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>CSRone</span><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>表示，<span lang='EN-US'>2019</span>年台灣共出版<span lang='EN-US'>556</span>本企業永續報告書，說明企業於<span lang='EN-US'>2018</span>年度的<span lang='EN-US'>CSR</span>作為。其中又以金融保險業、化學工業以及電子零組件業三大產業對<span lang='EN-US'>CSR</span>最為積極。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>另根據統計，台灣<span lang='EN-US'>2019</span>年營收百大企業之中，僅剩<span lang='EN-US'>9</span>家企業尚未出版永續報告。而獲得證交所與櫃買中心「第<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>屆公司治理評鑑」前<span lang='EN-US'>5%</span>公司，則還有<span lang='EN-US'>8</span>家企業（上市<span lang='EN-US'>1</span>家、上櫃<span lang='EN-US'>7</span>家）尚未出版企業永續報告。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><strong><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>ROE</span><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>連<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>年也高於台股平均表現</span></strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>研究報告同時顯示，出版永續報告的上市櫃公司，其<span lang='EN-US'>2019</span>年的<span lang='EN-US'>EPS</span>為<span lang='EN-US'>3.69</span>元，高於台股大盤的<span lang='EN-US'>2.49</span>元以及未出版報告書的<span lang='EN-US'>2.14</span>元，且為連續<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>年皆優於台股大盤，而且優勢有逐年擴大的態勢。而<span lang='EN-US'>ROE</span>也有相同的趨勢，出版永續報告書之上市櫃公司<span lang='EN-US'>ROE</span>為<span lang='EN-US'>8.66%</span>，高於台股大盤的<span lang='EN-US'>5.72%</span>以及未出版報告書的<span lang='EN-US'>4.50%</span>，<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>年來也都是如此。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>目前金管會規定，股本<span lang='EN-US'>50</span>億元以上的上市櫃公司以及與民生密切相關的食品、金融、化工等產業，每年必須出版企業社會責任（<span lang='EN-US'>CSR</span>）報告書。<span lang='EN-US'>CSRone</span>表示，對企業而言，出版報告書不僅符合法律規範，又可以提升企業品牌形象與聲譽、瞭解營運風險、創造差異化價值、盤點內部營運、落實節能減碳、延攬優秀人才與營運資訊透明等，可謂好處多多。以致國內企業多數願意每年花費<span lang='EN-US'>80</span>萬至<span lang='EN-US'>100</span>萬元編製，甚至多花<span lang='EN-US'>15</span>萬至<span lang='EN-US'>25</span>萬元取得第三方驗證，提高可信度。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>資料來源：<span lang='EN-US'>https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/paper/1361270</span></span></span></p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-03-25","clk_count":"164"}},"__N_SSG":true}